column12: No matter how things unfold, it all returns to us. All of it.
Sorry, guys... I think this is it for me, too.
Oh, quit crying. Look, before I go, we need to take care of this guy.
I want you to petrify me. You can use me to keep this thing locked away down there.
He's right! It's suicide! You can't do it!
Your powers exist to protect others, right?
If you don't, it's gonna break down this fucking door!
I...I don't know what to do...
